- [Stammers] Uh, Hildi in the hot box.

1218
01:31:37,828 --> 01:31:40,163
[Calvin] What's she doin' there?

1219
01:31:40,330 --> 01:31:42,999
[Stephen] What you think she
doin' there in the hot box?

1220
01:31:43,166 --> 01:31:45,669
She bein' punished.

1221
01:31:45,836 --> 01:31:48,338
- [Calvin] What she do?
- [Stephen] She run off again.

1222
01:31:48,505 --> 01:31:51,174
