1230
01:32:12,320 --> 01:32:15,365
[Calvin]
How long she been in the box?

1231
01:32:15,532 --> 01:32:19,453
[Stephen] How long you think
she been in there? All damn day.

1232
01:32:19,619 --> 01:32:20,579
