1269
01:36:47,804 --> 01:36:50,140
- [Chuckles]
- [Forced chuckle]

1270
01:36:52,142 --> 01:36:54,102
As I look at you now, Broomhilda,

1271
01:36:55,645 --> 01:36:57,814
I can see all the passions you inspire
