1304
01:41:35,508 --> 01:41:39,262
[All laugh]

1305
01:41:39,929 --> 01:41:42,015
Well, regardless, Samson's your best.
We all know that.

1306
01:41:42,181 --> 01:41:43,975
You will never sell him,
and I can see why. He's a champion.

1307
01:41:45,268 --> 01:41:46,769
Hm-hm.
All three are champions.

1308
01:41:46,936 --> 01:41:48,062
Samson's the champion.

1309
01:41:48,229 --> 01:41:50,314
Them other two pretty good.

1310
01:41:50,481 --> 01:41:53,860
Calvin, now what's
this nigger you let...

1311
01:41:54,027 --> 01:41:58,322
It's all right.

