01:41:58,489 --> 01:41:59,574
You have to understand,
Monsieur Candie,

1313
01:41:59,741 --> 01:42:03,828
while admittedly a neophyte
in the nigger fight game,

1314
01:42:03,995 --> 01:42:04,954
I do have a little bit of a background
in the European traveling circus.

1315
01:42:05,121 --> 01:42:07,582
Is that right?

1316
01:42:09,333 --> 01:42:11,544
