than just a big nigger.

1319
01:42:17,884 --> 01:42:21,095
Yeah, he needs to have panache.

1320
01:42:21,262 --> 01:42:22,889
- Need to have what? What?
- Panache. Uh...

1321
01:42:23,056 --> 01:42:24,432
- A sense of showmanship.
- Showmanship, yes.

1322
01:42:24,599 --> 01:42:25,600
