as the black Hercules.

1323
01:42:25,767 --> 01:42:27,894
[All chuckling]

1324
01:42:28,061 --> 01:42:33,441
The black Hercules,
isn't that clever?

1325
01:42:33,941 --> 01:42:36,736
More like nigger-les.

1326
01:42:36,903 --> 01:42:41,199
[Laughing]

1327
01:42:41,365 --> 01:42:44,077
