1329
01:42:46,913 --> 01:42:50,708
now I'm not saying that Eskimo Joe
is the wrong nigger, per se.

1330
01:42:50,875 --> 01:42:52,794
But is he right as rain?

1331
01:42:52,960 --> 01:42:54,712
Oh, Dr. Schultz,

1332
01:42:54,879 --> 01:42:55,880
