- Hm!

1360
01:44:10,329 --> 01:44:13,291
[Calvin] Nigger love's
a powerful emotion, boy.

1361
01:44:13,457 --> 01:44:15,001
- [Stephen] Hm!
- It's like a pool of black tar.

1362
01:44:15,168 --> 01:44:17,420
Once it catches your ass, you're caught.

1363
01:44:17,587 --> 01:44:22,091
Yessir, you stuck. [Laughs]

1364
01:44:23,217 --> 01:44:23,384
[Lara lee] I don't know, doctor.

1365
01:44:25,845 --> 01:44:26,012
You can lay on all the
German sweet talk you want,

1366
01:44:29,640 --> 01:44:29,807
but it looks like this pony's
got big eyes for Django.

1367
01:44:32,602 --> 01:44:32,769
[Lara Lee giggles]

1368
01:44:35,271 --> 01:44:35,438
Well, naturally.

1369
01:44:37,356 --> 01:44:37,523
It is the soaring eagle
that attracts her attention,

1370
01:44:38,566 --> 01:44:38,733
- not the plucked chicken.
- [All chuckle]

1371
01:44:40,735 --> 01:44:40,902
[Calvin] Dr. Schultz, don't be
so down on yourself.

1372
01:44:43,112 --> 01:44:44,030
