European gentleman.

1373
01:44:45,323 --> 01:44:45,490
[Cora] You got to clean these dishes,

1374
01:44:48,576 --> 01:44:50,328
you got to put your elbow
in these dishes, you hear me?

1375
01:44:52,330 --> 01:44:52,497
You know that nigger, don't you?

1376
01:44:53,748 --> 01:44:53,915
- Who?
- "Who?"

1377
01:44:56,959 --> 01:44:57,126
Don't "who" me, bitch.
You know who I'm talkin' about.

1378
01:44:59,962 --> 01:45:02,048
At the table?

1379
01:45:03,132 --> 01:45:04,592
