1380
01:45:07,053 --> 01:45:11,265
- You don't know him.
- No.

1381
01:45:12,475 --> 01:45:13,726
- "No," what?
- No, sir.

1382
01:45:16,854 --> 01:45:23,319
[Chuckles]

1383
01:45:26,739 --> 01:45:28,116
You wouldn't lie to me, now, would you?

1384
01:45:33,287 --> 01:45:33,454
Ok.

1385
01:45:35,790 --> 01:45:35,957
Yeah. If you say so.

1386
01:45:37,917 --> 01:45:38,084
Eskimo Joe's a quality nigger,
no doubt about it.

1387
01:45:41,546 --> 01:45:42,505
But if it was my money,
I wouldn't pay no $12,000 for him.

1388
01:45:45,758 --> 01:45:47,009
What would your price be?

1389
01:45:52,807 --> 01:45:52,974
Well, if I was inclined
to be generous...

1390
01:45:55,143 --> 01:45:55,309
