I would be inclined to be generous...

1391
01:45:56,269 --> 01:45:56,435
...9,000. Maybe.

1392
01:45:58,146 --> 01:45:58,312
Dr. Schultz, let me reclarify how
this whole negotiation came about.

1393
01:46:00,481 --> 01:46:00,648
You see, it wasn't me
who came to you to sell a nigger.

1394
01:46:03,067 --> 01:46:03,234
Sure wasn't.

1395
01:46:04,861 --> 01:46:05,027
It was you who approached me to buy one.

1396
01:46:07,989 --> 01:46:08,156
- Sure was.
- Now, that $9,000 figure

1397
01:46:12,410 --> 01:46:13,035
bright boy's been bandyin' about,
that ain't too far off from right.

1398
01:46:17,039 --> 01:46:17,206
And if I wanted to sell
Eskimo Joe for that,

1399
01:46:20,042 --> 01:46:24,714
