offer of $12,000

1402
01:46:33,764 --> 01:46:36,225
- that made me even consider it.
- Hm-mm.

1403
01:46:38,644 --> 01:46:38,811
[Deep inhale]

1404
01:46:42,148 --> 01:46:42,315
You know, Monsieur Candie,
you do possess the power of persuasion.

1405
01:46:44,442 --> 01:46:44,609
[Chuckles]

1406
01:46:48,154 --> 01:46:48,321
[Slamming table] Why not?
Monsieur Candie, you have a deal.

1407
01:46:51,490 --> 01:46:51,657
- Eskimo Joe, $12,000.
- [Banging table] Hooray, doctor.

1408
01:46:53,451 --> 01:46:53,618
Hooray.
And a wise decision that is.

1409
01:46:56,704 --> 01:46:56,871
However, that is
a tremendous amount of money.

1410
01:46:59,916 --> 01:47:00,082
And the way you have
your Mr. Moguy, I have a lawyer.

1411
01:47:01,083 --> 01:47:01,250
