Eskimo Joe examined

1416
01:47:16,474 --> 01:47:16,641
- by a physician of my choosing.
- [Calvin] Naturally.

1417
01:47:18,684 --> 01:47:18,851
So, say I return in about...

1418
01:47:21,812 --> 01:47:22,647
- ...five days time.
- Five days?

1419
01:47:25,691 --> 01:47:26,442
With my Mr. Tuttle.

1420
01:47:27,610 --> 01:47:28,611
And then my Mr. Tuttle
and your Mr. Moguy

1421
01:47:30,613 --> 01:47:32,990
