1425
01:47:43,834 --> 01:47:44,001
To Eskimo Joe.
Or shall we call him the black Hercules?

1426
01:47:47,838 --> 01:47:48,005
- [All chuckling]
- To the black Hercules.

1427
01:47:49,423 --> 01:47:49,590
[Stephen] The black Hercules.

1428
01:47:52,843 --> 01:47:55,930
[Speaks low]
To the black Hercules.

