gettin' to pleasure all them Mandingos,

1438
01:48:21,163 --> 01:48:21,330
- huh, sugar bear?
- Oh, lord, she like them niggers.

1439
01:48:25,001 --> 01:48:25,167
- Sure do.
- Like samson? Huh?

1440
01:48:28,421 --> 01:48:28,587
[Hildi] No, sir.

1441
01:48:30,715 --> 01:48:30,881
You know, Monsieur Candie,

